title: IDisplayDimension.GetOverride
description: Gets whether to display the actual dimension value or to override it with another value.
returns: True to display the override value, false to display the actual dimension value
remarks:
Use
IDisplayDimension::GetOverrideValue
to get the override value.
Use
IDisplayDimension::SetOverride
to set whether to override the actual dimension value with another value and, if so, that value.
